{"tid":118851,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"嵩山少林寺被日本忍者踢館 眾僧不敵大敗","createTime":"2017-02-13T10:17:53.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-22T09:01:53.000Z","uid":30788,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"37a5cbc2580571c1159831cb6dbbbf9a3330fabe","tid":118851,"uid":30788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T10:17:53.000Z","msg":"日本忍者打敗少林武僧？內地網上近日流傳尠一名日本資深忍者，到河南嵩山少林寺踢館，少林寺派武僧迎戰，結果日本忍者以自創的獨門拳法，擊敗武僧。對於有關消息少林寺方面予以否認。<br />\n<br />\n內地多個論壇近日出現「日本伊賀忍者少林踢館」的消息，發表文章的網民指出，一個名為山本義清的日本伊賀派資深忍者，本月5日抵達河南，當日凌晨身穿忍者服潛入少林寺，留下挑戰書，要求秘密切磋。少林寺接挑戰書後連夜商討，決定派武僧釋延的迎戰。<br />\n<br />\n少林監院：沒這回事<br />\n<br />\n發消息的網民稱，山本義清在深山習武三十年，五年前決定挑戰少林武僧，並且閉關研究出一種自創拳法。山本義清與釋延的在上周六（11日）凌晨三時在少林寺習武廳比武，「經過一番比試」，釋延的被打敗。山本義清在勝出後再留下戰書，揚言五年後會再次挑戰少林武僧。<br />\n<br />\n對於有關說法，少林寺監院釋延裕說：「壓根兒沒有這回事！」少林寺亦從沒接待過名叫山本義清的忍者。"},{"pid":"a8e8a959abb4fe46b8adeeb9101c9c63da032cb0","tid":118851,"uid":52215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T10:19:37.000Z","msg":"納dee出黎一掌打死個忍者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad1622c982af21a345f1c687d32c4762bead4211","tid":118851,"uid":45285,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T10:22:46.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">「經過一番比試」，釋延的被打敗。山本義清在勝出後再留下戰書，揚言五年後會再次挑戰少林武僧。</span><br />\n<br />\nWIN左五年後又去打係乜玩法？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f84b6e3335a4920aa91d4db18f4e7d1a2d4aa17","tid":118851,"uid":14423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T10:22:54.000Z","msg":"我信係假，因為少林寺唔會夠膽應戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4f8033ca029be832454c8f1658b99009f6b40fb8","tid":118851,"uid":67878,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T10:24:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"123cbd91366433b4ac7c4dcb9d57e11429f7037a","tid":118851,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T10:25:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我信係假，因為少林寺唔會夠膽應戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真正武憎去晒做城管<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"011729697f2a7b967914f4af610978502ad08944","tid":118851,"uid":51796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T10:25:45.000Z","msg":"十八銅人呢"},{"pid":"ec505f549e8b8bd5d4cb08ad06d3c1542ec3bf89","tid":118851,"uid":20177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T10:26:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我信係假，因為少林寺唔會夠膽應戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n真係既話少林寺點會唔開擂台，<br />\n收入場費賺返筆？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"157732cab113a3a1cf95f6a1910ab9d0fcec0146","tid":118851,"uid":6222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T10:31:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>十八銅人呢</blockquote><br />\n係中國廚藝學院同食神鋤緊Dee"},{"pid":"df985f1857c8b04fa4dc131bcf39822225796615","tid":118851,"uid":28068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T10:32:28.000Z","msg":"火影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b33d27e19e58956f87909300786fe067460994b4","tid":118851,"uid":1779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T10:35:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">「經過一番比試」，釋延的被打敗。山本義清在勝出後再留下戰書，揚言五年後會再次挑戰少林武僧。</span><br />\n<br />\nWIN左五年後又去打係乜玩法？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n俾五年時間你班垃圾練<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n下次再玩"},{"pid":"5cce704d3e53c98c5f44a382860be7190826c18f","tid":118851,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T10:44:53.000Z","msg":"Old news is so唔識串"},{"pid":"0d5782b3da87241ebc56dae808724d045a25562e","tid":118851,"uid":39365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-13T10:52:45.000Z","msg":"單新聞無廿年都有十年了<img src